title: How to Get the Here You Go Achievement on Cookie Clicker

steps.headline: Unlock the "What's in a name" achievement (optional).
steps.description: To unlock this achievement, you need to rename your bakery to whatever you choose, and right away you'll get this achievement. It's recommended to get this achievement first because in the Stats menu this achievement is just to the left of the "Here you go" achievement slot, so you can use this achievement as a compass.

steps.headline: Click on the correct achievement slot.
steps.description: This slot will be just to the right of the "What's in a name" achievement slot.

steps.headline: You unlocked the achievement!
steps.description: Wasn't that easy? Like other achievements, it will unlock upgraded milk, the most upgraded being Maple Milk.

text: Open up Cookie Clicker.  Unlock the "What's in a name" achievement (optional). To unlock this achievement, you need to rename your bakery to whatever you choose, and right away you'll get this achievement. It's recommended to get this achievement first because in the Stats menu this achievement is just to the left of the "Here you go" achievement slot, so you can use this achievement as a compass. Click on the correct achievement slot. This slot will be just to the right of the "What's in a name" achievement slot. You unlocked the achievement! Wasn't that easy? Like other achievements, it will unlock upgraded milk, the most upgraded being Maple Milk.
